    <section_number>8.07</section_number>
    <catch_line>Resignation Of Directors</catch_line>
    <order_by>8.07</order_by>
    <text>
        <section prefix="a">
    	     A director may resign at any time by delivering written notice of resignation to the board of directors, its chairman, or to the corporation.
        </section>
        <section prefix="b">
    	     A resignation is effective when the notice is delivered unless the notice specifies a later effective date.
        </section>
    </text>
</law>